            <p>
              SHPE Outreach has had a long history of fostering STEM awareness in High Schools. Bringing in students from across the country and a broad range of socioeconomic classes to experience the life of a U of I engineering student. We also have a broad array of SHPE members visit High Schools and bring STEM to students in the local Champaign-Urbana. The Shadow program brings together a High Schooler and an Undergraduate student, and lets the High School student follow and get experience in college life. 
